text: Carly Hannah Chaikin (born March 26, 1990) is an American actress. Her acting career began in 2009. She played Dalia Royce in the ABC sitcom Suburgatory. She played the role until the series' cancellation in 2014. She also played Darlene in the USA Network thriller drama series Mr. Robot. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Santa Monica, California
